{"tid":1167747,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[印尼武勇] 雅加達騷亂至少6死 六萬軍警進駐","createTime":"2019-05-23T08:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T09:28:01.000Z","uid":40980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5d7e7d36494eb67dedcde4abf33e206974c274","tid":1167747,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:57:33.000Z","msg":"今日 14:46 時事脈搏<br />\n<br />\n印尼選舉委員會周二(21日)公布上月大選的正式結果，宣布總統佐科(Joko Widodo)連任後，引起落敗候選人普拉博沃(Prabowo Subianto)的支持者不滿，在首都雅加達發動示威演變成騷亂，致6人死亡，約200人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，目前約6萬名軍警進駐雅加達，駐紮在包括選委會大樓和總統府等重要設施。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人透露，已拘捕超過300名示威者，當局現正審問他們；形容示威者主要來自雅加達以外，進入首都目的是為了製造騷亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/05/23/2144542_7f89c08c2bf9c42fb804f85d6cba2a78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F05%2F23%2F2144542_7f89c08c2bf9c42fb804f85d6cba2a78.jpg&h=abab9799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2144542/%E9%9B%85%E5%8A%A0%E9%81%94%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%916%E6%AD%BB+%E5%85%AD%E8%90%AC%E8%BB%8D%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E9%A7%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2144542%2F%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%258A%25A0%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%25916%25E6%25AD%25BB%2B%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2580%25B2%25E9%25A7%2590&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo6y4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=1c6c3f2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2144542/%E9%9B%85%E5%8A%A0%E9%81%94%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%916%E6%AD%BB+%E5%85%AD%E8%90%AC%E8%BB%8D%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%B2%E9%A7%90</a>"},{"pid":"37628e878225a2712a54b26271bac1cf5bc82a32","tid":1167747,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2144557/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%3A%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%9C%AA%E9%98%BB%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%B8%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2144557%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C%253A%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2598%25BB%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo6y4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=2bc83b2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2144557/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%3A%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E6%9C%AA%E9%98%BB%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%A6%82%E5%B8%B8%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n今日 15:20 國際財經<br />\n<br />\n印尼央行:騷亂未阻銀行體系如常運作<br />\n <br />\n放大圖片<br />\n外電報道，印尼央行行長瓦爾吉約(Perry Warjiyo)表示，雖然印尼首都雅加達自周二起發生公眾騷亂，但印尼銀行體系仍運作如常。他又稱，這些騷亂並未造成資本外流。<br />\n<br />\n瓦爾吉約指出，在發生動亂的地方，不只是銀行，其他活動也受到干擾，不過銀行體系運作仍然正常。<br />\n<br />\n重申支持印尼盾滙價承諾的瓦爾吉約亦表示，日前資金外流導致印尼盾跌至2019年新低，主要是受到外部因素影響，而不是受到雅加達騷亂事件影響。"}]}